  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK841">
<l>aṟiviṉmai yiṉmaiyu ḷiṉmai piṟitiṉmai</l>
<l>yiṉmaiyā vaiyā tulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The want of wisdom is the greatest of all wants but that of wealth the world will not regard as such.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
